            "description": {
              "description": "<div class='bbcode bbcode--normal-line-height'><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://i.ppy.sh/4d2b95c4d554827ecbcffaffabf9fa9acee9aee2/68747470733a2f2f66696c65732e636174626f782e6d6f652f306a396e766f2e706e67\" loading=\"lazy\" style=\"aspect-ratio: 1; width: 10px;\" class=\"js-gallery\" data-width=\"10\" data-height=\"10\" data-index=\"0\" data-gallery-id=\"371001636\" data-src=\"https://i.ppy.sh/4d2b95c4d554827ecbcffaffabf9fa9acee9aee2/68747470733a2f2f66696c65732e636174626f782e6d6f652f306a396e766f2e706e67\" /><br /><center><span style=\"font-size:150%;\"><span style=\"color:#E06290;\">₊°❀.ೃ࿔*</span> <strong><span style=\"color:#E06290;\">E</span><span style=\"color:#DF6E97;\">c</span><span style=\"color:#DF7A9F;\">h</span><span style=\"color:#DE86A6;\">o</span><span style=\"color:#DD92AD;\">e</span><span style=\"color:#DD9EB5;\">s </span><span style=\"color:#DCA9BC;\">o</span><span style=\"color:#DBB5C3;\">f </span><span style=\"color:#DAC1CA;\">a </span><span style=\"color:#DACDD2;\">B</span><span style=\"color:#D9D9D9;\">r</span><span style=\"color:#DAC8CC;\">o</span><span style=\"color:#DAB7BE;\">k</span><span style=\"color:#DBA6B1;\">e</span><span style=\"color:#DB95A3;\">n </span><span style=\"color:#DC8496;\">E</span><span style=\"color:#DC7388;\">a</span><span style=\"color:#DD627B;\">r</span><span style=\"color:#DD516D;\">t</span><span style=\"color:#DE2F52;\">h</span></strong> <span style=\"color:#DE2F52;\">‧₊˚❀༉‧₊˚.</span></span><br /><span style=\"font-size:100%;\"><strong><span style=\"color:#ffffff;\">Sillot</span></strong></span></center><br /><span style=\"font-size:85%;\"><iframe class=\"u-embed-wide u-embed-wide--bbcode\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/82rlyurMEyI?rel=0\" allowfullscreen=\"\"></iframe></span><br /><div class=\"well\"><center><span style=\"font-size:150%;\"><strong>MAP INFO</strong></span><br />🌸 ⋆─────────────⋆ ✧ ⋆─────────────⋆ 🌸<br />• A high-sr hybrid tiebreaker-styled map!<br />• mostly dump, tech, and density oriented around MWC25 4K GFTB diff.<br /><br /><span style=\"font-size:80%;\">Collaboration with <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://osu.ppy.sh/users/10072733\"><strong><span style=\"color:#fb7f65;\">myucchi<u>i</u></span></strong></a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://osu.ppy.sh/users/15513303\"><strong><span style=\"color:#48EADD;\">Z</span><span style=\"color:#55C3E0;\">n</span><span style=\"color:#629CE4;\">o</span><span style=\"color:#7557E0;\"><u>w</u></span></strong></a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://osu.ppy.sh/users/21340543\"><strong><span style=\"color:#8482E6;\">Naiib<u>e</u></span></strong></a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://osu.ppy.sh/users/30357961\"><strong><span style=\"color:#E28A93;\">Alumenc<u>e</u></span></strong></a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://osu.ppy.sh/users/25868133\"><strong><span style=\"color:#FBF0DC;\">Kagetayor<u>i</u></span></strong></a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://osu.ppy.sh/users/18270260\"><strong><span style=\"color:#B8CF53;\">Hylot<u>l</u></span></strong></a>, and <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://osu.ppy.sh/users/13094831\"><strong><span style=\"color:#6057EF;\">Blue_Potio<u>n</u></span></strong></a>.<br /><br /><em>piano E♭ <del>power chord</del> perfect octave jumpscare</em></span><br /><br /><span style=\"font-size:80%;\">Map made for the <span style=\"color:#FD5D67;\">4K Mania Chilean <u>Tournament</u> 2026</span>;<br />Grand Finals Tiebreaker.</span><br />🌸 ⋆─────────────⋆ ✧ ⋆─────────────⋆ 🌸</center></div><br /><div class=\"well\"><center><span style=\"font-size:125%;\"><span style=\"color:#FFFFFF;\"><strong>------- ≪• 🌸 GOODIES BOX</strong> 🌸 •≫ -------</span></span><br /><span style=\"font-size:85%;\">➤ <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://soundcloud.com/manu_gmr-22\"><span style=\"color:#ffa938;\">Sillot</span><span style=\"color:#FFFFFF;\">'s <u>SoundCloud</u> <img alt=\"\" src=\"https://i.ppy.sh/6f3114205a5e3d1ba4bf8ad847baf23b40cafc5c/68747470733a2f2f66696c65732e636174626f782e6d6f652f3574717975322e706e67\" loading=\"lazy\" style=\"aspect-ratio: 1; width: 16px;\" class=\"js-gallery\" data-width=\"16\" data-height=\"16\" data-index=\"2\" data-gallery-id=\"371001636\" data-src=\"https://i.ppy.sh/6f3114205a5e3d1ba4bf8ad847baf23b40cafc5c/68747470733a2f2f66696c65732e636174626f782e6d6f652f3574717975322e706e67\" /></span></a></span><br /><span style=\"font-size:85%;\">➤ <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://soundcloud.com/manu_gmr-22/echoes-of-a-broken-earth\"><span style=\"color:#FFFFFF;\">SoundCloud </span><span style=\"color:#ffa938;\">song</span> <span style=\"color:#FFFFFF;\"><u>link</u></span> <img alt=\"\" src=\"https://i.ppy.sh/6f3114205a5e3d1ba4bf8ad847baf23b40cafc5c/68747470733a2f2f66696c65732e636174626f782e6d6f652f3574717975322e706e67\" loading=\"lazy\" style=\"aspect-ratio: 1; width: 16px;\" class=\"js-gallery\" data-width=\"16\" data-height=\"16\" data-index=\"2\" data-gallery-id=\"371001636\" data-src=\"https://i.ppy.sh/6f3114205a5e3d1ba4bf8ad847baf23b40cafc5c/68747470733a2f2f66696c65732e636174626f782e6d6f652f3574717975322e706e67\" /></a></span><br /><span style=\"font-size:85%;\">➤ <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://x.com/mochaomg/status/2028617253642436978\"><span style=\"color:#FFFFFF;\">Thanks </span><span style=\"color:#BEADEA;\">mohca</span> <span style=\"color:#FFFFFF;\">for the <u>typography</u></span> <img alt=\"\" src=\"https://i.ppy.sh/7ea5f049f7a11d4536de48a82bde579bb76b2039/68747470733a2f2f66696c65732e636174626f782e6d6f652f72717a6667362e706e67\" loading=\"lazy\" style=\"aspect-ratio: 1.2308; width: 16px;\" class=\"js-gallery\" data-width=\"16\" data-height=\"13\" data-index=\"3\" data-gallery-id=\"371001636\" data-src=\"https://i.ppy.sh/7ea5f049f7a11d4536de48a82bde579bb76b2039/68747470733a2f2f66696c65732e636174626f782e6d6f652f72717a6667362e706e67\" /></a></span><br /><br /><span style=\"font-size:85%;\"><em><span style=\"color:#FFC3A5;\">hope you enjoy ( ´ ▽ ` )ﾉ</span></em></span><br /></center></div></div>"
